    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Divinis flammeis <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>visionib</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> frequenter <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>admonit</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> et virtutis magnae mai<lb break="no" n="3"/>iestatis martyrii caelestium <expan><abbr>virgin</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>imminentium ex <expan><abbr>partib</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> orientis <lb n="5"/>exsibitus pro voto Clematius <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ir</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>larissimus</ex></expan> de <lb n="6"/>proprio in loco suo hanc basilicam <lb n="7"/>voto quod debebat a fundamentis <lb n="8"/>restituit si quis autem super tantam <lb n="9"/>maiiestatem <note>sic</note> huiius <note>sic</note> basilicae ubi sanc<lb break="no" n="10"/>tae virgines pro nomine XP<expan><ex>Chris</ex><abbr>t</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> san<lb break="no" n="11"/>guinem suum fuderunt corpus alicuiius <note>sic</note> <lb n="12"/>deposuerit exceptis <expan><abbr>virginib</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> sciat se <lb n="13"/>sempiternis tartari <expan><abbr>iginib</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> puniendum
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Datierung: &amp;quot;&amp;quot;4.-5. Jh. (W. Levison, BJb 132, 1927, 3-25) oder karlingische Zeit&amp;quot;&amp;quot; (Galsterer - Galsterer); &amp;quot;&amp;quot;litterae non sunt aetatis Constantini sed saeculi XV …&amp;quot;&amp;quot; (CIL).</p>
            </div>
